		<item name="wcf.acp.option.hytale_linker_enabled"><![CDATA[Activate Hytale-Linker]]></item>
		<item name="wcf.acp.option.hytale_linker_enabled.description"><![CDATA[<p>Enables/disables Hytale-Linker.</p>
<p>Links for plugin configuration:</p>
<p><kbd>sendCode: {link controller='HytaleLinkerCode' forceFrontend=true}{/link}</kbd></p>
<p><kbd>updateNames: {link controller='HytaleLinkerUpdateName' forceFrontend=true}{/link}</kbd></p>
<p><kbd>getLinked: {link controller='HytaleLinkerGetLinked' forceFrontend=true}{/link}</kbd></p>
<p><kbd>getUnlinked: {link controller='HytaleLinkerGetUnlinked' forceFrontend=true}{/link}</kbd></p>]]></item>
		<item name="wcf.acp.option.hytale_linker_identity"><![CDATA[Server]]></item>
		<item name="wcf.acp.option.hytale_linker_identity.description"><![CDATA[Enables Hytale-Linker for selected servers.]]></item>
		<item name="wcf.acp.option.hytale_max_uuids"><![CDATA[Maximum number of Hytale-Links per user]]></item>
		<item name="wcf.acp.option.suffix.mc_uuids"><![CDATA[Links]]></item>
		<item name="wcf.acp.option.hytale_enable_active_user"><![CDATA[Activate user]]></item>
		<item name="wcf.acp.option.hytale_enable_active_user.description"><![CDATA[<p>Activates a user if they have added a Hytale linker shortcut.</p>
<p>For this option to work properly, the option <kbd>{'wcf.acp.option.register_activation_method'|language}</kbd> must be set to <kbd>{'wcf.acp.option.register_activation_method.byAdmin'|language}</kbd > or <kbd>{'wcf.acp.option.register_activation_method.byUserAndAdmin'|language}</kbd> must be set.</p>]]></item>
		<item name="wcf.acp.option.hytale_enable_disable_user"><![CDATA[Deactivate user]]></item>
		<item name="wcf.acp.option.hytale_enable_disable_user.description"><![CDATA[<p>Deactivates a user if they no longer have a Hytale Linker shortcut.</p>
<p>Administrators and users with the <kbd>{'wcf.acp.group.option.user.hytaleLinker.mandatory'|language}</kbd> permission will not be deactivated.</p>
<p>It is recommended to use modify the phrases <kbd>wcf.user.register.needAdminActivation</kbd>, <kbd>wcf.user.register.success.awaitActivation</kbd> and <kbd>wcf.user.registerActivation.success.awaitAdminActivation</kbd>.</p>]]></item>
	</category>
